    public class GrowingVPAlphabet<I>
extends AbstractVPAlphabet<VPSym<I>>
implements VPAlphabet<VPSym<I>>
    A VPAlphabet implementation that allows to add new symbols after its construction. Wraps input symbols in a VPSym instance to allow faster mappings from symbols to indexes.
